### **Step 3: Images You MUST Add (Visual Assets)**

Aapko **yeh 6 images minimum** add karni hain:

| # | Image Name | What to Show | Priority |
|---|-----------|-------------|----------|
| 1 | `dashboard-kpi.png` | Full dashboard with KPI cards (Headcount, Salary, Forecast Accuracy, Shrinkage, Occupancy, SL, AHT, CSAT, QA) | ⭐ Critical |
| 2 | `forecast-vs-actual.png` | Monthly bar chart — Forecast vs Actual calls | ⭐ Critical |
| 3 | `sl-trend.png` | Daily Service Level % line chart (Jun 1-14) | ⭐ Critical |
| 4 | `lob-analysis.png` | Shrinkage % & Service Level % by LOB (bar chart) | ⭐ Critical |
| 5 | `data-cleaning-before-after.png` | Split image showing raw vs cleaned data sample | Medium |
| 6 | `pivot-table-sample.png` | One pivot table screenshot (By LOB or By Site) | Medium |
| 7 | `risk-matrix.png` | Top 5 risks visual (heatmap or priority matrix) | Nice to have |
| 8 | `recommendations-timeline.png` | 10 recommendations with timeline/impact | Nice to have |

